(243, 1, '2023-04-20 02:26:34', '2023-04-20 09:26:34', 'Asus Gaming ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W laptop puts on an impressive, powerful Gaming appearance suitable for gamers. This will be a good candidate with the ability to meet the needs of using common tasks quickly, and promises to bring you a great experience in each game.\r\nAsus Gaming Laptop ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W\r\nStylish gaming look, the keyboard is equipped with a brilliant RGB LED system\r\nAsus Gaming ROG Strix has a stylish design with square chassis lines that show strength, along with LED contours for a bold gaming style. The company\'s logo is slanted stylized to create accents for the product. Taking gray as the main color gives the laptop a luxurious and mysterious appearance.\r\n\r\nAsus Gaming Laptop ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W | Design bold gaming\r\nAsus laptops are equipped with a standard-sized keyboard that is easy to use. Deep key travel and premium construction materials provide a more comfortable, precise typing experience. RGB LEDs provide illumination so you can operate the keyboard well in low-light environments. The responsive touchpad makes it easy to control the machine smoothly and quickly as you like.\r\n\r\nAsus Gaming Laptop ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W | Keyboard\r\nHigh-quality display screen, convenient anti-glare technology\r\nROG Strix Gaming Laptop is equipped with a large 15.6-inch screen with a resolution of 1920 x 1080px for sharp, realistic images. The IPS panel offers a 144Hz refresh rate for smooth moving frames with brilliant color reproduction.\r\n\r\nAsus Gaming Laptop ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W | Screen\r\nThe screen is also covered with an anti-glare layer with the function of limiting the influence of direct light on the image quality. From there you can enjoy beautiful frames from any angle. The screen is designed with thin bezels to enhance the aesthetics and provide a wider viewing angle.\r\n\r\nPowerful configuration with AMD Ryzen 7, NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050Ti 4GB GDDR6 graphics card\r\nAMD Ryzen 7 processor gives Asus laptops a powerful performance. With a basic structure of 8 cores, 16 threads, providing a clock speed of 2.9GHz - 4.2GHz thanks to Turbo Boost mode to quickly handle most tasks from basic to advanced.\r\n\r\nAsus Gaming Laptop ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W | Graphics card, performance\r\nNVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050Ti 4GB GDDR6 graphics card for impressive graphics processing. With this line of cards, Asus Gaming ROG Strix laptops let you be creative with graphics software for high performance. You can also experience your favorite games with realistic images, smooth motion.\r\n\r\nEnhance multitasking with 8GB DDR4 3200MHz RAM, large storage space with 512GB\r\n8GB DDR4 3200MHz RAM gives Asus laptops the ability to multitask to improve efficiency at the same time. You can comfortably open many tabs to study and work without worrying about lag, thereby helping to improve work and study efficiency.\r\n\r\nAsus Gaming Laptop ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W | Storage memory\r\nThe 512GB SSD M.2 NVMe hard drive provides a spacious storage space where you can comfortably store the necessary applications or personal information without worrying about overload. In addition, this line of hard drives also supports the Asus Gaming ROG Strix laptop significantly in increasing the speed of machine startup and data access.\r\n\r\nLong battery life, pre-installed Windows 11 Home operating system\r\nAsus laptops are equipped with a built-in battery with a capacity of 4 cells 56 Wh. This battery is capable of providing you with a long life to meet the needs of entertainment as well as work.\r\n\r\nAsus Gaming Laptop ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W | The battery\r\nThe pre-installed Windows 11 Home operating system allows you to use the machine as soon as you buy it without having to pay installation fees. Windows 11 provides you with a wide range of utility applications and advanced security capabilities to protect your privacy.\r\n\r\nAsus Gaming Laptop ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W | Windows 11\r\nFully equipped with modern connection ports, convenient wireless connection technology\r\nThe Asus laptop is fully equipped with modern connectivity ports such as HDMI output port, USB Type C / DisplayPort / Power Delivery ports, 3 x USB 3.2, 1 Gb/s LAN allowing you to connect Connect to multiple peripherals easily.\r\n\r\nAsus Gaming Laptop ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W | Connector\r\nWireless connectivity standards include WiFi 802.11ax (Wifi 6), Bluetooth 5.1 providing a stable high-speed transmission and easy connection to mobile devices for fast data transmission.', 'Laptop ASUS Gaming ROG Strix G513IE-HN246W (Ryzen 7 4800H/RAM 8GB/512GB SSD/ Windows 11)', '- CPU: AMD Ryzen 7 4800H\r\n- Screen: 15.6\" IPS (1920 x 1080), 144Hz\r\n- RAM: 1 x 8GB DDR4 3200MHz\r\n- Graphics: RTX 3050Ti 4GB GDDR6 / AMD Radeon Graphics\r\n- Storage: 512GB SSD M.2 NVMe /\r\n- Operating system: Windows 11 Home\r\n- Battery: 4 cells 56 Wh Instant battery\r\n- Weight: 2.1kg', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'laptop-asus-gaming-rog-strix-g513ie-hn246w-ryzen-7-4800h-ram-8gb-512gb-ssd-windows-11-2', '', '', '2023-04-23 18:20:14', '2023-04-24 01:20:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=243', 0, 'product', '', 0),
