(271, 1, '2023-04-23 18:02:41', '2023-04-24 01:02:41', '<h2>The set of 4 versions of iPhone 12 still has its charm that has not cooled down, but Apple gives users a new super product iPhone 13 with many interesting improvements that promise to bring the most attractive experiences to users. use.</h2>\r\n<h3>Luxurious design, more class in appearance</h3>\r\nThe iPhone 13 has a square monolithic design like its predecessor, the frame is made of aluminum, luxurious beauty with a high-grade glass back. The appearance is not very different from its predecessor, but the screen-to-body ratio is better.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_81a30583-e04f-4257-a4c8-30307980b31d.jpeg\" alt=\"Thiết kế sang trọng\" /></figure>\r\nThe notch of this version 13 is about 20% smaller to increase the experience area when surfing the web, watching movies or playing games. Machine weight 174g, thickness only 0.765 cm.\r\n\r\nThe biggest difference in appearance that helps create a distinctive, new and beautiful, more luxurious identity point is probably the camera sensors that are placed diagonally instead of lined up like the iPhone 12. Color\r\n\r\nMidnight luxury, iPhone 13 certified for IP68 water and dust resistance for peace of mind.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_2a5bf057-c702-43b8-877d-924895ebe526.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Thiết kế sang trọng đẳng cấp\" /></figure>\r\n<h3>Excellent Super Retina XDR display, high brightness, save battery</h3>\r\niPhone 13 with 6.1-inch screen size, using OLED panels for vivid color quality and sharp image details, resolution up to 2532 x 1170 px. The oleophobic layer is coated on the outside of the screen to help limit the user\'s dirt and sweat.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_058d0488-10e7-4a61-841d-da0baa3f0076.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Màn hình retina mạnh mẽ\" /></figure>\r\nTop notch Super Retina XDR screen technology helps to achieve 800 nits brightness, up to 1200 nits maximum, P3 wide color range, good color stability and image display quality in low light or sunny conditions. harsh, glare with great contrast ratio.\r\n<h3>Powerful performance thanks to Apple A15 Bionic chip</h3>\r\niPhone 13 has extremely impressive performance with the super powerful Apple A15 Bionic chip manufactured on the 5 nm process, about 50% faster CPU performance, about 30% faster GPU than competitors in the same category. segment.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_a15d87e6-3270-4f7e-8738-ba2726157b2b.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Hiệu năng mạnh mẽ\" /></figure>\r\nImproved performance for users to get a better experience on the phone when using entertainment applications, editing photos, videos or can fight games with high graphics with the most stability and smoothness. maybe. The iPhone 13 is equipped with 128 GB of internal memory that is ideal for storage enjoyment.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_4ef7237b-e269-4c7c-9538-c27486dece1e.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Bộ nhớ trong 128gb\" /></figure>\r\nThe 5G mobile network standard is enhanced with superior bandwidth, with 5G making it possible for phones to stream or download quickly. Not stopping there, this super product has a smart data mode that automatically detects and reduces the network speed to help save energy when not using high speed.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_12205a2b-fa99-4099-8ab8-fd218ea29119.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Hiệu năng mạnh mẽ\" /></figure>\r\n<h3>The pinnacle of cinema with outstanding dual camera clusters</h3>\r\niPhone 13 is equipped with a dual rear camera cluster with 12 MP resolution, the image quality is improved compared to its predecessor with the ability to capture light of the main camera up to 47%. The ultra-wide-angle camera offers a 120-degree field of view to capture more details, easily capturing majestic mountain memories or group photos.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_e7717644-2e00-460d-ba83-f11278134a50.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Chụp ảnh đỉnh cao\" /></figure>\r\nSensor Shift optical stabilization is also included in this 13 version to help focus quickly, night photography becomes clear with less noise, and video recording is also very stable and smoother. The front camera is still located in the notch, the resolution also reaches 12 MP with the latest photography technologies such as bokeh effect, cinema mode, Memoji and Animoji.\r\n<h3>Improved battery life - Innovative charging technology</h3>\r\nAccording to Apple\'s announcement, this version 13 has an increased battery life of about 2.5 hours compared to its predecessor, for longer use time to serve more effectively for users with high frequency of use.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_d8d4299e-c4de-45cb-a913-4b73324bc15d.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Tối ưu hóa năng lượng\" /></figure>\r\nSupports 20W fast charging capable of charging 50% of the battery in just 30 minutes. Lithium battery technology, MagSafe and Qi advanced wireless charging technology. Lightning charging port, quality Nano SIM and eSIM sim cards. Lightning type headphone jack. Efficient wifi connection Wi‑Fi 6 (802.11ax) with MIMO. Connect to modern GPS GPS, GLONASS, Galileo, QZSS, BeiDou.\r\n\r\nSee also: iPhone 13 Pro max, iPhone 14\r\n<h3>Buy Genuine iPhone 13 128GB Midnight Mobile Phone| Phong Vu warranty up to 12 months</h3>\r\niPhone 13 brings class to any individual who owns and enjoys the ultimate experience of using a smartphone. Buy iPhone at Phong Vu to receive peace of mind with genuine quality, great warranty policy and attractive shopping incentives.', 'iPhone 13 | Genuine VNA', '- Genuine, New 100%, Original seal\r\n- Screen: 6.1\" - Super Retina XDR OLED\r\n- Rear camera: 2x 12MP\r\n- Front camera: 12MP\r\n- CPU: Apple A15 Bionic\r\n- Memory: 256GB\r\n- Operating system: IOS', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'iphone-13-genuine-vna', '', '', '2023-04-27 01:30:24', '2023-04-27 08:30:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=271', 0, 'product', '', 0),
