(280, 1, '2023-04-23 18:25:46', '2023-04-24 01:25:46', '<h2>Laptop MacBook Air 2020 13.3\" MGN93SA/A is a high-end laptop from the famous Apple brand.The new generation Macbook Air possesses exquisite beauty and powerful performance from the Apple M1 chip. The laptop is suitable for many users for work and entertainment.</h2>\r\n<h3>Luxurious silver design, high quality lightweight durable material</h3>\r\nLaptop MacBook Air 2020 13.3\" MGN93SA/A brings luxury beauty thanks to its beautiful silver exterior design. Details around the laptop are meticulously and delicately finished. The Macbook Air series is designed with simplicity in mind. but still ensure to bring the inherent modern beauty.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/7/13/20220713_e2ab66f8-3538-4d92-b154-ec60cefa9961.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop MacBook Air 2020 13.3&quot; MGN93SA/A | Thiết kế gọn gàng \" /></figure>\r\nApple\'s new generation laptop is made of lightweight materials that are durable. As a result, the weight of the laptop is kept at about 1.3 kg. This is one of the outstanding advantages that help the Macbook Air line always receive the favor of many users because of its compactness and ease of portability.\r\n<h3>Powerful performance with M1 chip, 13.3\" IPS . screen</h3>\r\nMacBook Air 2020 13.3\" laptop MGN93SA/A works smoothly with high speed and quickly processes all information thanks to a super powerful M1 chip.M1 is an 8-core processor, complete based on 5 nm architecture The chip will deliver faster performance on the Macbook line.\r\n\r\nThis is a new generation chipset released by Apple itself and promises to bring outstanding performance to effectively improve the configuration of Macbook lines. Powered by up to 16 billion transistors, the M1 can deliver 3.5x faster CPU performance, and 6x faster GPU performance.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/7/13/20220713_d1c168e2-35c9-4cfc-9c85-ac7f3faba176.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop MacBook Air 2020 13.3&quot; MGN93SA/A | Sử dụng văn phòng, đồ họa mượt mà \" /></figure>\r\nAt the same time, the new MacBook with integrated M1 chip also means that the battery life will also be up to 2 times longer than the previous generation Macbook lines. This is really good news for Apple fans.\r\n\r\nTalking more about the M1 chip, the inside chip will include 8 cores, with 4 high-performance cores and 4 power-saving cores. Heavy tasks such as playing games or graphic design, editing video and images, .. the M1 chip will take advantage of all the power coming from the CPU to meet the above usage needs.\r\n\r\nIn the case when you only use the laptop to watch movies, listen to music, surf the web, light entertainment, the remaining 4 power-saving cores will be utilized, from which the using time of the Macbook will be extended. more.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the powerful chipset, the MacBook Air 2020 13.3\" MGN93SA/A is also supported by 8GB RAM for bus speeds up to 3733MHz, so the laptop will be able to multitask with multiple software at the same time while ensuring the operation process. Motion takes place smoothly, there is no lag.\r\n\r\nIn terms of storage capacity, the MacBook Air 2020 13.3\" MGN93SA/A laptop has a 256GB hard drive. With a large amount of storage, you will easily be able to bring the miniature entertainment world in Macbook anywhere.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/7/13/20220713_a27f1ab5-38d2-4117-b667-1c2978cbd7ab.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop MacBook Air 2020 13.3&quot; MGN93SA/A | Dung lượng lớn, khởi động nhanh \" /></figure>\r\nRegarding the screen, the MacBook Air 2020 13.3\" MGN93SA/A has a 13.3-inch screen with a modern IPS panel for wide viewing angles. realistic and vivid way with many bright and rich colors.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/7/13/20220713_ac8eb9e1-7248-4485-aa0f-611c6b560b66.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop MacBook Air 2020 13.3&quot; MGN93SA/A | Màn hình sắc nét \" /></figure>\r\n<h3>Equipped with modern connection ports, LED-supported keyboard</h3>\r\nIn terms of connectivity, the MacBook Air 2020 13.3\" MGN93SA/A includes 2 Thunderbolt 3 ports for fast and efficient data transfer so that users can share information in a very short time.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/7/13/20220713_a7f4f613-0aaa-44bc-b0c7-961b9836193b.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop MacBook Air 2020 13.3&quot; MGN93SA/A | Cổng kết nối hiện đại \" /></figure>\r\nThe keyboard of the MacBook Air 2020 13.3\" MGN93SA/A  is designed with enough space for convenient user operation. The keys are smooth, have good bounce and high response speed. In addition, the light part. LED helps users to see better in low light conditions.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/7/13/20220713_9e7ce14c-7f80-4c2d-b5f8-341b946d2c5c.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop MacBook Air 2020 13.3&quot; MGN93SA/A | Bàn phím êm ái, Bảo mật vân tay \" /></figure>\r\n<h3>Buy genuine MacBook Air 2020 13.3\" MGN93SA/A laptop in Phong Vu | Prestigious long-term warranty</h3>\r\nThe MacBook Air 2020 13.3\" MGN93SA/A laptop with many outstanding features will bring the quality of use worthy of the Apple brand. Come to Phong Vu to buy products and enjoy a reliable long-term warranty!', 'MacBook Air 2020 13.3 inch MGN93SA/A (M1/8GB/SSD/256GB)', '- CPU: Apple M1\r\n- Screen: 13.3\" IPS (2560 x 1600)\r\n- RAM: 8GB Onboard LPDDR4 3733MHz\r\n- Graphics:\r\n- Storage: 256GB SSD /\r\n- Operating system: macOS\r\n- Instant battery\r\n- Weight: 1.3kg', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'macbook-air-2020-13-3-inch-mgn93sa-a-m1-8gb-ssd-256gb-2', '', '', '2023-04-23 18:42:11', '2023-04-24 01:42:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?post_type=product