(286, 1, '2023-04-23 19:15:30', '2023-04-24 02:15:30', '<h2>Headphones Logitech H150 (White) many modern technologies at a reasonable price</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logitech H150 (Trắng) | giá thành hợp lí\" /></figure>\r\n<h3>Overview of the Logitech H150 . Headset</h3>\r\n<h3>ENJOY HOURS OF INTERNET CALLS AND LISTEN TO MUSIC FROM COMPUTER WITH CLEAR, CLEAN SOUND.</h3>\r\nFlexible and adjustable, for computers that use separate 3.5mm audio and microphone jacks. In-line controls let you adjust the volume or mute calls without interrupting. Noise canceling microphone reduces background noise.\r\n<h3>main function</h3>\r\n(Pictures of the same type and color are for illustrative purposes of the product)\r\n\r\n1. STRUCTURE\r\n\r\nFull stereo sound delivers crystal clear, clear quality for voice, video calls, music, games and more. Stereo headphones for both personal use or in the office.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng1.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logitech H150 (Trắng) | ÂM THANH NỔI\" /></figure>\r\n2. Swivel MICRO\r\n\r\nThe mic boom can be rotated 180° to be worn on the left or right side. The flexible mic can be conveniently positioned for better voice capture and background noise reduction. The mic boom folds inside the strap for a neat look when you\'re not using it.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng2.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logitech H150 (Trắng) | MICRÔ XOAY\" /></figure>\r\n<figure class=\"image\">\r\n3. ONLINE CONTROL BUTTON\r\n\r\nConveniently located controls on the headset cord allow you to adjust the volume or mute calls without interruption.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng3-1.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logitech H150 (Trắng) | NÚT ĐIỀU KHIỂN TRÊN DÂY\" /></figure>\r\n4. ADJUSTABLE STRAP\r\n\r\nRugged yet lightweight stereo headphones with wide range of adjustments. Super soft foam earpads provide hours of comfort.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng4.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logitech H150 (Trắng) | QUAI ĐEO CÓ THỂ ĐIỀU CHỈNH ĐƯỢC\" /></figure>\r\n5. CONNECTING BY 2 CONNECTORS\r\n\r\nConnect to computers using separate 3.5mm audio jacks for both mic jacks and audio out. Not compatible with Chromebook™, tablets or Macs.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng5.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logitech H150 (Trắng) | KẾT NỐI BẰNG 2 GIẮC CẮM\" /></figure>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBuy Genuine Logitech H150 Headset (White) | Phong Vu 24 months warranty\r\n\r\nLogitech H150 (White) headset is sold at a mid-range, affordable price for students. When buying here, you will receive many unexpected incentives and support up to 2 years warranty. So what are you waiting for, visit the website Phong Vu to order and wait for the attractive offers!', 'Logitech H150 On-ear Headset (White)', '- Design: On Ear (covered over the ear)\r\n- Connection: Jack 3.5mm (audio) / Jack 3.5mm (mic)\r\n- Functions: Volume Control / Microphone Mute\r\n- \"Office\" headset is suitable for office users, listening to music, watching movies, learning foreign languages', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'logitech-h150-on-ear-headset-white', '', '', '2023-04-23 19:15:31', '2023-04-24 02:15:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=286', 0, 'product', '', 0),
